'''[[孟加拉|孟加拉]]'''參與8次夏季[[奥林匹克运动会|奥林匹克运动会]]。未曾參與冬季奧運。

2016年，西迪庫爾·拉赫曼以自身條件獲得高爾夫球的賽事資格<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://indianexpress.com/sports/rio-2016-olympics/golfer-siddikur-rahman-becomes-first-bangladesh-player-to-qualify-for-olympics-2910010/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-01-06 |archive-date=2020-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611043856/https://indianexpress.com/sports/rio-2016-olympics/golfer-siddikur-rahman-becomes-first-bangladesh-player-to-qualify-for-olympics-2910010/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及歷屆最多的7人參與該屆賽事。該國過去幾屆都以[[外卡|外卡]]方式獲得資格而得以過去7屆奧運不缺席。<ref name=swing>[http://english.cri.cn/2886/2008/06/15/53@369141.htm "Bangladesh's Preparation for Beijing Olympics in Full Swing"] {{Wayback|url=http://english.cri.cn/2886/2008/06/15/53@369141.htm |date=20191114221205 }}. ''Xinhua''. June 15, 2008.</ref>

孟加拉人口約1億7000萬，是至今未獲得任何獎牌的國家中人口最多的，人口比其多的國家已經經獲得不少獎牌。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/mikemehalick/the-10-most-populated-countries-to-never-win-an-ol|title=The 10 Most Populous Countries To Never Win An Olympic Medal|work=BuzzFeed Community|accessdate=22 February 2016|archive-date=2017-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921194031/https://www.buzzfeed.com/mikemehalick/the-10-most-populated-countries-to-never-win-an-ol|dead-url=no}}</ref>

孟加拉奧會主席為[[Wali_Ullah|Wali Ullah]]表示孟加拉的經濟偏差使現在體育運動方面的成果不佳。<ref name=swing/>

